title: Yemaya
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Yemaya offers organic, vegetarian and vegan dishes including pasta and desserts, combining foods from different regions. Flavorful large dishes costing 6 dollars on average, pleasant and friendly staff, clean, decorated and spacious set-up. They also always have exhibitions of paintings and photos from local artists.
